{
  "texts": [
    "However, there are free and publicly available datasets, such as ASAP and ASAP++, which lack feedback associated with the scores.",
    "This work presents the challenges and research directions in AES.",
    "We have highlighted the limited research on feedback generation in essay scoring.",
    "We hypothesize that the gap in feedback generation for AES may be attributed to the scarcity of annotated datasets that include feedback and traits.",
    "However, recent studies (Han et al. 2023a) have demonstrated that the augmentation of large language models can alleviate the challenge of limited feedback in datasets."
  ]
}